      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the risk part but i feel like the people on the forums know what they're doing. mcm if i just do it for like 14 days it shouldn't really mess up my blood calcium levels right? i'm pretty healthy and dont have any kidney issues, so it feels like a quick way to just fix the deficit. isnt most of it just water soluble anyway so my body will just pee out the extra?",
